         <div type="commentary">
            <p>The text is clearly part of a civic decree concerned with measures taken against barbarian invaders, 
               presumably the Marmaridae of the Augustan period.  <!-- see Introduction, XXX  --></p>
            <p>Line 16. The earliest instance so far of this nomenclature.</p>
            <p>Line 18. Probably the god Ammon but possibly a man with the name Ἀμμωνιος</p>
         </div>
         
